        Data class representing a read-only model of the class Appointment Entity, with some additional information to display on the client-side

        Parameters:
        id - the Appointment's id
        startTime - the Appointment's start time
        endTime - the Appointment's end time
        telescopeId - the Appointment's associated telescope id
        isPublic - the Appointment's flag indicating if it is public or not
        userId - the Appointment's associated user id
        userFirstName - the Appointment owner's first name
        userLastName - the Appointment owner's last name
        status - the Appointment's Status
